-kopa-actor-profile-and-biography/ |archive-date=2016-08-04 |df= }}</ref><ref name=\"MB\" />\n\n==Career==\nSudhi started off doing small roles in multi-starer movies. He played a goon attacking [[Bhavana (Malayalam actress)|Bhavana]] in ''[[Sagar Alias Jacky Reloaded]]'' and one of the students in ''[[Seniors (film)|Seniors]]'' (2011). His theater background helped him secure a role in [[Lijo Jose Pellissery]]'s ''[[Amen (2013 film)|Amen]]''. He played the role of Solomon's friend Sebastian, who tries to woo Solomon's sister played by [[Rachana Narayanankutty]].<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/malayalam/movies/news/M-Towns-own-booze-playlist/articleshow/48556134.cms |title=M- Town\u2019s own booze playlist |website=Timesofindia.indiatimes.com |date=2015-08-21 |access-date=2016-12-24 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160219135324/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/malayalam/movies/news/M-Towns-own-booze-playlist/articleshow/48556134.cms |archive-date=2016-02-19 |df= }}</ref> He then played many more small roles in ''[[Manglish (film)|Manglish]]'' and ''[[Sapthamashree Thaskaraha]]'' (2014).\n\nHis breakthrough came in ''[[Aadu (film)|Aadu]]'' (2015), in which he played \"Kanjavu\" Soman.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/it-not-honey-rose-srinda-who-plays-lead-aadu-oru-bheegara-jeeviyanu-615434 |title=It is Not Honey Rose but Srinda Who Plays the Lead in 'Aadu Oru Bheegara Jeeviyanu' |website=Ibtimes.co.in |date=2014-11-28 |access-date=2016-12-24 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105223558/http://www.ibtimes.co.in/it-not-honey-rose-srinda-who-plays-lead-aadu-oru-bheegara-jeeviyanu-615434 |archive-date=2016-11-05 |df= }}</ref> The double-crossing Soman served as an important link between the different story tracks in the movie. He subsequently played an important role as the naive Unni in ''[[You Too Brutus (film)|You Too Brutus]]'' (2015).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nowrunning.com/movie/16511/malayalam/you-too-brutus/5027/review/ |title=You Too Brutus Review - Malayalam Movie You Too Brutus nowrunning review |website=Nowrunning.com |date=2015-03-22 |access-date=2016-12-24 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105223723/http://www.nowrunning.com/movie/16511/malayalam/you-too-brutus/5027/review/ |archive-date=2016-11-05 |df= }}</ref>\n\n2016 saw a string of releases in which he had good roles. He played Darwin's henchman Appunni in ''[[Darvinte Parinamam]]'' (2015). He was then seen as Hari and Manu's friend Paul Achayan in ''[[Happy Wedding]]'' (2016).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/happy-wedding-completes-101-days-heres-worldwide-box-office-collection-surprise-hit-photos-690873 |title='Happy Wedding' completes 101 days; here's worldwide box office collection of the surprise hit [PHOTOS&#93; |website=Ibtimes.co.in |date=2016-08-23 |access-date=2016-12-24 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170218184903/http://www.ibtimes.co.in/happy-wedding-completes-101-days-heres-worldwide-box-office-collection-surprise-hit-photos-690873 |archive-date=2017-02-18 |df= }}</ref> He then portrayed the alcoholic Thanka in ''[[Anuraga Karikkin Vellam]]'' (2016), who gets into fights with Abhi and friends.<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/malayalam/movies/news/Asif-is-Biju-Menons-son-in-his-next/articleshow/49014378.cms |title=Asif is Biju Menon\u2019s son in his next! |website=Timesofindia.indiatimes.com |date=2015-09-19 |accessdate=2016-12-24}}</ref> He also essayed the role of a comical thief, Kaimal aka Kai in [[Sajid Yahiya]]'s directorial debut ''[[Inspector Dawood Ibrahim|IDI: Inspector Dawood Ibrahim]]'' (2016).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nowrunning.com/idi-inspector-dawood-ibrahim-shoot-progressing/119445/story.htm |title='IDI - Inspector Dawood Ibrahim' shoot progressing |website=Nowrunning.com |date=2016-04-02 |access-date=2016-12-24 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160601103736/http://www.nowrunning.com/idi-inspector-dawood-ibrahim-shoot-progressing/119445/story.htm |archive-date=2016-06-01 |df= }}</ref> He was last seen as one of Asif Ali's teammates in ''[[Kavi Uddheshichathu..?]]'' (2016).\n\nHe is currently working on ''Third World Boys'', a road movie and ''Theeram''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nowrunning.com/theeram-started-rolling/117771/story.htm |title='Theeram' started rolling |website=Nowrunning.com |date=2016-02-17 |access-date=2016-12-24 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319210529/http://www.nowrunning.com/theeram-started-rolling/117771/story.htm |archive-date=2016-03-19 |df= }}</ref> He is also playing a major role in ''[[Avarude Raavukal]]'' (2017), starring [[Asif Ali (actor)]] and [[Unni Mukundan]], and directed by Shanil Muhammed, who had earlier co-directed ''[[Philips and the Monkey Pen]]'' (2013).\nHe also acted in a small role alongside superstar [[Manju Warrier]] in ''[[Udaharanam Sujatha]]'' (2017), which brought him lot of praise and went on to be a critical and commercial success.\n\n==Filmography==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Film !! Role !! Notes\n|-\n| 2009 || ''[[Sagar Alias Jacky Reloaded]]'' || Attacker||\n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[Mummy & Me]]'' || College Student||Uncredited Role\n|-\n| 2011 || ''[[Seniors (film)|Seniors]]'' || College Student||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2013 || ''[[North_24_Kaatham|North 24 Kaatham]]'' || Toddy Shop Patron ||\n|-\n|''[[Amen (2013 film)|Amen]]'' || Sebastian ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2014 || ''[[Manglish (film)|Manglish]]'' || Sahadevan ||\n|-\n|''[[Sapthamashree Thaskaraha]]'' || Gee Varghese ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" | 2015 || ''[[Aadu (film)|Aadu]]'' || Kanjavu Soman || \n|-\n|''[[You Too Brutus (film)|You Too Brutus]]'' || Unni   ||\n|-\n|''[[Love 24x7]]'' || Joshy ||\n|-\n|''[[KL 10 Patthu]]'' || Nizam ||\n|-\n|''[[Lord Livingstone 7000 Ka