b-cast/|title=Brittany Lauda Joins \u2018Holy Knight\u2019 Anime Dub Cast|author=|date=January 29, 2015|work=fandompost.com|accessdate=October 19, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fandompost.com/2015/01/23/mb-voiceworks-to-produce-english-language-dubs-for-media-blasters-anime/|title=MB VoiceWorks To Produce English-Language Dubs For Media Blasters Anime|author=|date=January 23, 2015|work=fandompost.com|accessdate=October 19, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Ladies versus Butlers]]'' || Kaoru Daichi || ADR Director || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2015-07-25/media-blasters-adds-more-ladies-vs-butlers-dub-cast-streams-clips/.90884|title=Media Blasters Adds More Ladies vs. Butlers Dub Cast, Streams Clips|author=|date=|work=animenewsnetwork.com|accessdate=June 13, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fandompost.com/2015/09/30/ladies-versus-butlers-anime-gets-new-dub-clip/|title=\u2018Ladies Versus Butlers\u2019 Anime Gets New Dub Clip|author=|date=September 30, 2015|work=fandompost.com|accessdate=October 19, 2016}}</ref><ref name=\"con profile\">{{cite web|url=http://connecticon.org/guests/category/anime|title=ConnectiCon|author=|date=|work=connecticon.org|accessdate=June 13, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[List of Pok\u00e9mon: XY episodes|Pok\u00e9mon: XY]]'' || Katherine, Charlene, Lily || || Resume\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[Gosick]]'' || Luigi || || Resume\n|-\n| 2017-2019 ||''[[The Morose Mononokean]]''|| Yahiko ||also season 2\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-11-06/the-morose-mononokean-english-dub-trailer-streamed/.123663|title=The Morose Mononokean's English Dub Trailer Streamed|website=Anime News Network|language=en|access-date=2019-05-30}}</ref><ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[Castle Town Dandelion]]'' || Anzu Shirogane || || <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.funimation.com/blog/2016/09/19/english-cast-announcement-castle-town-dandelion/|title=English Cast Announcement - Castle Town Dande